efining relevant processes and tools to operate at scale Talent development: Develop and nurture a team of marketing professionals QUALIFICATIONS Track-record as a marketing leader with measurable impacts and tangible achievements Ability to build and manage high performing marketing teams 7 - 12+ years of experience in crypto, fintech or financial services marketing Fluency in English required Bachelor's degree required; Master\u2019s degree preferred About You Team player/coach \u2013 CoinDesk is a medium sized company that operates as a closely held subsidiary of the Digital Currency Group. Must be flexible, entrepreneurial, and demonstrate a \u201ccan do\u2019 attitude with all colleagues throughout the DCG family Excellent communication skills, both written and oral with the ability to negotiate with peers and colleagues in a confident and compelling manner ???? Inspirational leader; can motivate, inspire and galvanize teams. ???? Start-up experience strongly preferred; entrepreneurial spirit a must Excellent interpersonal skills, ability to manage, mentor and motivate a team. Emotional intelligence is critical to this role ???? Strong analytical and logical skills ???? Problem-solving and organizational skills ???? Strong presentation skills ???? Strong track record in thriving in a high energetic, fast moving environment ???? An extremely smart and dynamic individual with outstanding communication skills and a balanced egoShow moreShow less ", 
